Text: REQUEST: FULLY WORKING MADDOG 2.1 for FSX
Dickweeds.  No-one seems to know how to say thank you except dickxxx.  Anyway, thanx for the up spiders96.
This didn't work well for me. The VC was all messed up - gauges working but the panel was reflective and see-through. Other Carenado aircraft that I've downloaded from TPB have worked fine.
I agree with MechwarriorPuppies, the panel is transparent and all messed up. Shame, but thanks for the effort.
